RECONSIDERATION OF PRIOR DECISIONS

2012-2173. King v. King.

Medina App. Nos. 11CA0006-M, 11CA0023-M, and 11CA0069-M, 2012-Ohio-5219. Reported at 134 Ohio St.3d 1507, 2013-Ohio-1123, 984 N.E.2d 1101. On motion for reconsideration of Christopher D. King. Motion denied. On motions to dismiss of Elizabeth A. King and Christopher D. King. Motions denied as moot.
